Description
===========
Library Management web application how to create a Spring MVC 4.3 application with Spring Data MongoDB and AngularJs.Validate form data client side with AngularJs Captcha.

Technologies used:
=====
Spring MVC 4.3
MondoDB
AngularJs v1.2.28
Mockito for testing
Bootstrap 3.3.5

Heroku

You can access to the web app that deployed heroku

http://mysterious-crag-9770.herokuapp.com/books
